Walk around the counter top
Take the plate in the table
Move to near the sink
Put the plate in the sink, clean it off
Take back in the sink

Pick up the plate from the counter top.
Turn left to reach the sink.
Wash the plate in the sink and take it out.
Turn left to reach the sink counter.
Put the plate on the sink counter.

high_descs: Move, turn right, walk up to fridge, turn right, move towards the counter top.
Take the plate from the counter top.
Put the plate into the sink, wash it, take back the plate.
Put the plate on the left corner of the sink table.
anns.task_desc: To take the plate from counter top, wash it, put it on the sink table.
